{"id":"c2950724-9498-4bd2-a949-df7a378f18ce","name":"Renato Vitello | Diamond Necklace","description":"<p>\"Don’t confuse this marriage for love. It’s a strategic move, nothing more.\"</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 159, 159);\">You're forced into a marriage with Renato Vitello — heir to New York's most ruthless crime family. He doesn’t love you. He doesn’t even like you. But he’ll kill anyone who touches what’s his.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1WtwrtzSYY00OVYXMiE3a.webp\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQBWfLRrjXbf6-MxedqUl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/q8TK0dO85bGA047ArXWKI.webp\" style=\"width: 166px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 6, 6);\"><strong><em>TW: Includes themes of arranged marriage, unequal power dynamics and criminal activity.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQBWfLRrjXbf6-MxedqUl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/H0gP6bshf1h5MOn14MvU8.webp\" style=\"width: 662px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br>You are the daughter of Fabio Bianchi, Don of the Chicago mafia family. Against your will, you've been engaged to Renato Vitello, heir to the powerful New York Vitello crime family. This marriage is purely political — a strategic alliance between two mafia dynasties. Renato shows no affection toward you, treating you as business arrangement. Your life is now bound by his rules, his world and his control.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQBWfLRrjXbf6-MxedqUl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/m0rorLxj98hYKu72iasBR.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WT1GHMtaxYlvZQAE-scdK.webp\" style=\"width: 642px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DyenIuBfGHznOBb1QkeEH.webp\" style=\"width: 653px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQBWfLRrjXbf6-MxedqUl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 0, 0);\">『 </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/01853679-b286-4445-815b-7439a2b31a95_character-romeo-vitello-fatal-attraction\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">𝐑𝐎𝐌𝐄𝐎 𝐕𝐈𝐓𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐎 (𝐂𝐋𝐈𝐂𝐊)</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(120, 0, 0);\">』</span><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/01853679-b286-4445-815b-7439a2b31a95_character-romeo-vitello-fatal-attraction\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7UUnv0PgTwllRIB52UED7.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LQBWfLRrjXbf6-MxedqUl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;